oved\r\n- added the 'panrgp' workflow. It will probably replace the main 'workflow' command in the future but for the next few versions, they will live side by side.\r\n- improved logging and added timing at the end of the 'panrgp' workflow.\r\n\r\npangenomes that were computed with previous versions should be compatible with the new commands."}
{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/releases/22079825", "assets_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/releases/22079825/assets", "upload_url": "https://uploads.github.com/repos/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/releases/22079825/assets{?name,label}", "html_url": "https://github.com/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/releases/tag/1.0.13", "id": 22079825, "author": {"login": "axbazin", "id": 30264003, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMwMjY0MDAz", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/30264003?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin", "html_url": "https://github.com/axbazin", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/axbazin/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "node_id": "MDc6UmVsZWFzZTIyMDc5ODI1", "tag_name": "1.0.13", "target_commitish": "master", "name": "PPanGGOLiN release 1.0.13", "draft": false, "prerelease": false, "created_at": "2019-12-01T13:28:28Z", "published_at": "2020-01-22T10:32:48Z", "assets": [], "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/tarball/1.0.13", "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/zipball/1.0.13", "body": "- Better handling of input files (will raise errors before doing anything if any name is duplicated or if any input file does not exist)\r\n- Added the '--defrag' option to use the [defragmentation](https://github.com/labgem/PPanGGOLiN/wiki/PPanGGOLiN---step-by-step-pangenome-analysis#defragmentation) pipeline in the 'workflow' command (rather than having to use each subcommand separately only to use this option)\r\n\r\nBugfixes :\r\n\r\n- --soft-core option in 'evolution' and in 'write' commands actually works now when you change it\r\n- Cope with .gbk/.gbff files with : \r\n   - duplicate 'locus_tag' fields within assemblies and between different assemblies (happens when genomes are downloaded from Genbank) (fix for #25 ) \r\n   - no contig identifier in VERSION field (happens with Prokka annotated genomes)\r\n\r\n "}
